{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_10_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 アイドルのお手本に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらくした頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Some time after Moon Tempest became part of the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1699.9999284,
          "startTime": 1.6999999284
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふー……やっと休憩だ～\nあ、{user}さん、お疲れ様～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Finally‚ a break~!\nAh‚ {user}-san‚ thanks for your hard work~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それは俺のセリフだよ\n最近多忙だが、大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's my line.\nYou've been really busy lately. Are you alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7333340246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "このぐらい平気だよ！\nむしろもっと頑張れるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is nothing to me!\nI might even be able to do more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6666679937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "元気が有り余ってるなら何よりだ\nでも、無理だけはしないでくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have energy to spare‚ that's great.\nBut don't push yourself too hard‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってから、沢山仕事が舞い込んできてるが\n一番大事なのは芽衣の体だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been getting a lot of work since becoming BIG4‚ but\nyour health is the most important‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.1666654507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "休みたい時はちゃんと言うから大丈夫！\nいろんなお仕事がい～っぱい出来て、凄く楽しいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be sure to tell you when I want to rest‚ so it's alright!\nI can do all sorts of jobs‚ it's really fun‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "今度新曲のMV撮影もあるでしょ？\nそれに出るまでは倒れたりしないよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and we have a music video shoot for our new song too‚ right?\nI won't collapse before that~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2666608732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "MV撮影もいいが\nその後にある、番組出演のことも忘れないでくれよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The music video shoot is good and all‚ but\ndon't forget about the TV appearance after that‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！\n月ストの特集を組んでくれるんだったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nThey're putting together a Moon Tempest special‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7666608732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。それで、番組側から芽衣達に\nアンケートを書いてほしいと依頼がきてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. And so‚ the station asked\nMei and the others to fill out a questionnaire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "特に、『今後の目標について』の欄は\n番組内でも触れる可能性が高いそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In particular‚ the \"future goals\" section\nis likely to be brought up on the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0999991099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1666562955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "今後の目標か～……んー、なんだろう？\nご飯をいっぱい食べる！　とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Future goals… Hmm‚ what could it be?\nTo eat a whole bunch of rice! Or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333309173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.9999896288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "だ、ダメという訳じゃないんだが\nもう少し深い内容の方がいいと思うぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it's not that bad‚ but\nI think you should choose something with a little more substance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "「BIG4になった今、これからどうしていくのか」\nってことを、みんな聞きたいだろうからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Now that you are BIG4 ‚ what will you do next\"\nis what everyone wants to hear‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4333214362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になった今……これから……\nむむむ、難しいなぁ……急には思いつかないかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that I'm BIG4…… what will I do…\nHmm‚ it's hard~… I don't think I can come up with anything right away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0666657765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "他のみんなはどんな目標を立ててるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of goals have the others set?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5999881029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.1666547696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今ちょうど書いてもらっているところだよ\n特に悩んでいる様子はなかったが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're writing them down right now\nThey don't seem to be particularly worried‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.8666547696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、確かにBIG4にはなったけど\nなんかまだ実感がわかないんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For Mei‚ it's true that I became BIG4‚ but\nI still can't really believe it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "前の芽衣と比べて、変わってたりするのかなぁ？\n目つきがちょっと鋭くなったとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if I've changed compared to the Mei from before?\nLike my eyes have gotten a bit sharper?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.7666547696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "外見的には特に変わってないよ\nそうだなぁ、それなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's not much difference in appearance.\nWell‚ if that's the case…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.8333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、今後やってみたいことを考えてみたらどうだ？\n何か取っ掛かりを掴めるかもしれないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ why not think about what you want to try in the future?\nYou might be able to get a handle on something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8666547696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　したいことなら一杯あるよ！\n全部書きたいけど、何がいいかな～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! There are tons of things I want to do!\nI want to write them all down‚ but what would be good~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "早起きは出来るようになりたいし\n料理ももっとうまくなりたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be able to wake up early‚\nand I want to get better at cooking too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.9000094652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "プライベートなこともいいが\n仕事についても、掘り下げてみるといいかもな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine to have personal goals‚ but\nit might be good to focus more on work-related ones.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
